Have any of you other creators experienced something like this? 
I think as a creator when you put in so much of your time & effort into making a branded piece only to feel like all of that is going to waste can be so overwhelming sometimes. 
In my opinion if the brand did not want to go ahead with me, they could have informed me instead of ghosting my team & me after all the back and forth we did to get the best possible outcome of the video.

Would love to hear your experience in the comments below🫶🏻🫶🏻
